	(60,66,'Amazon','B000TKDQ5C','','Anonymous User','Lasko 754200 Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat','lasko-ceramic-adjustable-thermostat','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Lasko Ceramic Heater is a self-regulating ceramic space heater (with options for manual control). This space heater is a great option for those who require a little extra heat in a concentrated space, offering overheat protection, three basic heating options, (with an additional option to switch to a basic fan) and carrier handle for easy transport. Users give this product 4 out of 5 stars, claiming it is great for small rooms and easy to use.</span></p><p class=\"p1\">. Heats a small room very well (with 1500-watt high setting, 900-watt low setting, and fan-only option)</p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Includes multiple built in safety features, including, (but not limited to): automatic overheating sensors and turnoff. </p><p class=\"p1\"><b>. </b>Very easy to use and transport</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Lasko\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"754200\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"LCP-002\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Silver\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"9.2 X 7 X 6 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"7.1 X 7.9 X 10.8 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"4 Pound\"}]',35.99,18.63,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Lasko-754200-Ceramic-Adjustable-Thermostat/dp/B000TKDQ5C%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB000TKDQ5C','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3.5,\"counter\":4}]','3.5','','0','','Active','Best Lasko Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat','The Lasko Ceramic Heater is a tabletop heater for your room or office. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews, comparisons, vs, and lowest price on the Lasko Ceramic Heater.','\"\"','Usually ships in 24 hou